    All Classes and Interfaces

    Class
    Description
    AddColumnCommand
    Command handler for adding a new column to an existing table.
    AggregateCommand
    Command handler for performing aggregate operations (sum, product, min, max) on a numeric column for rows matching a search criterion.
    Application
    The main entry point for the Database CLI.
    CLI
    Handles the command line interface for the database application.
    CloseCommand
    Command handler for closing the currently open database catalog.
    Column
    Represents a column in a database table, including its name and data type.
    CommandHandler
    An interface for command handlers.
    CountCommand
    Command handler for counting rows in a table that match a specific criterion.
    CreateTableCommand
    Command handler for creating a new table in the database.
    Database
    Manages the database, including its catalog of tables, loaded tables in memory, and tracking unsaved changes.
    DatabaseOperationException
    Custom exception class for errors that occur during database operations.
    DataType
    Enumerates the supported data types for table columns.
    DeleteCommand
    Command handler for deleting rows from a table based on a specific criterion.
    DescribeCommand
    Command handler for displaying the structure (schema) of a table.
    ExitCommand
    Command handler for exiting the application.
    ExportCommand
    Command handler for exporting a table's data to a specified file.
    FileHandler
    Handles reading and writing database catalog files and table data files.
    HelpCommand
    Command handler for displaying help information about available commands.
    ImportCommand
    Command handler for importing a table from a text file into the database.
    InnerJoinCommand
    Command handler for performing an inner join operation on two tables.
    InsertCommand
    Command handler for inserting a new row of data into a table.
    OpenCommand
    Command handler for opening a database catalog file.
    PrintCommand
    Command handler for displaying the contents of a table with pagination.
    RenameCommand
    Command handler for renaming an existing table in the database.
    Row
    Represents a single row of data in a table.
    SaveAsCommand
    Command handler for saving the current database (catalog and all modified tables) to a new specified catalog file path.
    SaveCommand
    Command handler for saving the current state of the database (catalog and modified tables) to its existing file paths.
    SelectCommand
    Command handler for selecting and displaying rows from a table that match a specific criterion.
    ShowTablesCommand
    Command handler for displaying a list of all tables registered in the current database catalog.
    Table
    Represents a table in the database, consisting of a name, a list of columns, and a list of rows.
    TypeParser
    Utility class for parsing string values into specific data types and for comparing values with a degree of type flexibility.
    UpdateCommand
    Command handler for updating values in rows of a table that match a specific criterion.
